&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: 12.0pt;&quot;&gt;After Isaac is born, Abraham sends Hagar away with Ishma&apos;el while the feast in honour of the newborn Isaac is taking place in the background. The protecting angel hovers above the scene. (Genesis 21:8-11)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
