&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The Cartouch on the bottom right is surrounded by the figures of Moses and Aaron. Moses, had just descended from Mt. Sinai with the Tablets and is shown according to Jerome&apos;s mistaken translation of Exodus 34:29, with horns over his head. Next to him stands Aaron, the High Priest in his special attire and paraphernalia.&amp;#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
