&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;DefaultStyle&quot; style=&quot; margin-left: 35.45pt;&quot;&gt;Having found out belatedly about the sale, two important scholars were resolved to purchase the papers. The first was the famous British economist, John Maynard Keynes, who strove to buy all the alchemical papers; the second was the Jerusalem born well-known Orientalist, &lt;b&gt;Abraham Shalom Yahuda&lt;/b&gt;. At some point, they even exchanged some of the papers between them!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;DefaultStyle&quot; style=&quot; margin-left: 35.45pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
