&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;ul type=&quot;circle&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Born in Cordoba in 1138, Maimonides grew up during &amp;#160;the rule of the Berber dynasty&amp;#160; of the &lt;i&gt;Murabitun&lt;/i&gt; (Almoravids). Under their rule the Jewish and the Christian communities&amp;#160; were protected according to Muslim law.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Born in Cordoba in 1138, Maimonides grew up during &amp;#160;the rule of the Berber dynasty&amp;#160; of the &lt;i&gt;Murabitun&lt;/i&gt; (Almoravids). Under their rule the Jewish and the Christian communities&amp;#160;were protected according to Muslim law.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt;&lt;html xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;&gt;
