font-family: Arial;  font-size: small;  background: #ffffff;  color: #000000;
}
p {
margin-top: 0pt;  margin-bottom: 0pt;
}
--&gt;
&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;DefaultStyle&quot; style=&quot; margin-left: 21.3pt;&quot;&gt;Newton&apos;s preoccupation with the Apocalypse of John elicited this realistic map of the Near East which illustrates the geography of the region in which the Apocalyptic events will occur. According to Revelation 9 four angels will be released on the Euphrates river and will punish the sinners. Newton believed that the Fifth Trumpet is Islam, and the Sixth &#8211; the Ottoman Empire and identified as these four angels in the Sultanates marked out on the map&lt;b&gt;: Iconium, Damascus, Mosul and Miapharekin&lt;/b&gt;,.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;DefaultStyle&quot; style=&quot; margin-left: 21.3pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color: #2F3699;&quot;&gt;&#1511;&#1497;&#1513;&#1493;&#1512; &#1500;&#1488; &#1506;&#1493;&#1489;&#1491; (&#1500;&#1491;&#1497;&#1490;&#1497;&#1496;&#1493;&#1500;) &#1502;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dlib.nli.org.il/view/action/nmets.do?DOCCHOICE=NEWTON-008.xml&amp;#38;dvs=1383229721551~927&amp;#38;locale=en_US&amp;#38;search_terms=&amp;#38;adjacency=&amp;#38;VIEWER_URL=/view/action/nmets.do?&amp;#38;DELIVERY_RULE_ID=5&amp;#38;divType=&amp;#38;usePid1=true&amp;#38;usePid2=true&quot;&gt;http://dlib.nli.org.il/view/action/nmets.do?DOCCHOICE=NEWTON-008.xml&amp;#38;dvs=1383229721551~927&amp;#38;locale=en_US&amp;#38;search_terms=&amp;#38;adjacency=&amp;#38;VIEWER_URL=/view/action/nmets.do?&amp;#38;DELIVERY_RULE_ID=5&amp;#38;divType=&amp;#38;usePid1=true&amp;#38;usePid2=true&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt;&lt;html xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
&lt;meta name=&quot;generator&quot; content=&quot;EditLive! 7.6.2.10&quot; /&gt;
&lt;meta name=&quot;generator&quot; content=&quot;TheBrain 7.0.4.5&quot; /&gt;
